(42, 1, '2019-07-21 21:20:39', '2019-07-21 20:20:39', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The test page to check everyting is working as intended.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Test 1', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-21 21:20:39', '2019-07-21 20:20:39', '', 16, 'http://localhost:8888/heartsandminds/16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(43, 1, '2019-07-22 19:57:16', '2019-07-22 18:57:16', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hearts &amp; Minds Limited is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people with disabilities. We are continually improving the user experience for everyone, and applying the relevant accessibility standards.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Conformance status</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) defines requirements for designers and developers to improve accessibility for people with disabilities. It defines three levels of conformance: Level A, Level AA, and Level AAA. Hearts &amp; Minds is partially conformant with WCAG 2.1 level AA. Partially conformant means that some parts of the content do not fully conform to the accessibility standard. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Feedback</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of Hearts &amp; Minds. Please let us know if you encounter accessibility barriers on Hearts &amp; Minds:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>E-mail: info@heartsminds.org.uk </li><li>Postal address: Lower Ground, 4 Castle Terrace, Edinburgh, EH1 2DP</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We try to respond to feedback within 5 business days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Accessibility statement', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'accessibility-statement', '', '', '2019-07-22 20:01:32', '2019-07-22 19:01:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/heartsandminds/?page_id=43', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(44, 1, '2019-07-22 19:57:16', '2019-07-22 18:57:16', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hearts &amp; Minds Limited is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people with disabilities. We are continually improving the user experience for everyone, and applying the relevant accessibility standards. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Conformance status</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) defines requirements for designers and developers to improve accessibility for people with disabilities. It defines three levels of conformance: Level A, Level AA, and Level AAA. Hearts &amp; Minds is partially conformant with WCAG 2.1 level AA. Partially conformant means that some parts of the content do not fully conform to the accessibility standard. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Feedback</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of Hearts &amp; Minds. Please let us know if you encounter accessibility barriers on Hearts &amp; Minds:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>E-mail: info@heartsminds.org.uk </li><li>Postal address: Lower Ground, 4 Castle Terrace, Edinburgh, EH1 2DP</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">We try to respond to feedback within 5 business days. </pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->', 'Accessibility statement', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '43-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-22 19:57:16', '2019-07-22 18:57:16', '', 43, 'http://localhost:8888/heartsandminds/43-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(46, 1, '2019-07-22 20:00:09', '2019-07-22 19:00:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hearts &amp; Minds Limited is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people with disabilities. We are continually improving the user experience for everyone, and applying the relevant accessibility standards.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Conformance status</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) defines requirements for designers and developers to improve accessibility for people with disabilities. It defines three levels of conformance: Level A, Level AA, and Level AAA. Hearts &amp; Minds is partially conformant with WCAG 2.1 level AA. Partially conformant means that some parts of the content do not fully conform to the accessibility standard. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Feedback</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of Hearts &amp; Minds. Please let us know if you encounter accessibility barriers on Hearts &amp; Minds:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>E-mail: info@heartsminds.org.uk </li><li>Postal address: Lower Ground, 4 Castle Terrace, Edinburgh, EH1 2DP</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We try to respond to feedback within 5 business days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Accessibility statement', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '43-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-22 20:00:09', '2019-07-22 19:00:09', '', 43, 'http://localhost:8888/heartsandminds/43-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(49, 1, '2019-07-24 20:51:06', '2019-07-24 19:51:06', '', 'card', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'card', '', '', '2019-07-24 20:51:06', '2019-07-24 19:51:06', '', 16, 'http://localhost:8888/heartsandminds/wp-content/uploads/card.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
